<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
      .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
      .button { display: inline-block; background: #28a745; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
      .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 14px; }
      .info { background: #d1ecf1; border: 1px solid #bee5eb; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Confirm Your Email Address</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello <%= @user.name %>!</h2>
      
      <p>Thank you for signing up with ScheduleEase! To complete your registration and access all features, please confirm your email address.</p>
      
      <div class="info">
        <strong>Why confirm your email?</strong><br>
        Email confirmation helps us keep your account secure and ensures you receive important notifications about your appointments.
      </div>
      
      <p>Click the button below to confirm your email address:</p>
      
      <p>
        <a href="<%= @confirmation_url %>" class="button">Confirm Email Address</a>
      </p>
      
      <p>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
      <p style="word-break: break-all; background: #f8f9fa; padding: 10px; border-radius: 3px; font-family: monospace;">
        <%= @confirmation_url %>
      </p>
      
      <p>If you didn't create an account with ScheduleEase, please ignore this email.</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>The ScheduleEase Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Â© <%= Date.current.year %> ScheduleEase. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This email was sent to <%= @user.email %> because this address was used to create a ScheduleEase account.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html> 